question.string: How many spouses do head of states have on average?

    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>

    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/>

    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT (AVG(?countSpouses) AS ?averageSpouses) WHERE {
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256.
  ?country p:P35 ?statement.
  ?statement ps:P35 ?headOfState.
  OPTIONAL {
    ?headOfState wdt:P26 ?spouse.
    {
      SELECT ?headOfState (COUNT(?spouse) AS ?countSpouses) WHERE {
        ?headOfState wdt:P26 ?spouse.
      } GROUP BY ?headOfState
    }
  }
} GROUP BY ?country

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
    PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
    PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT (COUNT(?painting) AS ?count)
WHERE {
  ?painting wdt:P31 wd:Q3305213;      # instances of painting
            wdt:P170 wd:Q5593.        # created by Pablo Picasso
  ?museum wdt:P31 wd:Q33506;          # instances of museum
          wdt:P276 ?painting.         # location of painting
}

question.string: how many plays has William Shakespeare written in the 16th century.

query.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
    PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
    PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT (COUNT(?play) AS ?countPlays)
WHERE {
  ?play wdt:P31 wd:Q25379; # instance of play
        wdt:P50 wd:Q692. # written by William Shakespeare
  ?play wdt:P571 ?date. # inception date
  FILTER (YEAR(?date) >= 1501 && YEAR(?date) <= 1600) # filter plays written in the 16th century
}

question.string: Did Germany have a population growth of at least 1% since 2010?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
    PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
    PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
ASK {
  {
    SELECT (MAX(?population2010) as ?maxPopulation2010) {
      wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?popStatement2010.
      ?popStatement2010 ps:P1082 ?population2010.
      ?popStatement2010 pq:P585 ?date2010.
      FILTER(YEAR(?date2010) = 2010)
    }
  }
  {
    SELECT (MAX(?populationRecent) as ?maxPopulationRecent) {
      wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?popStatementRecent.
      ?popStatementRecent ps:P1082 ?populationRecent.
      ?popStatementRecent pq:P585 ?dateRecent.
      FILTER(YEAR(?dateRecent) >= 2010)
    }
  }
  BIND((?maxPopulationRecent - ?maxPopulation2010) / ?maxPopulation2010 * 100 AS ?growthPercentage)
  FILTER(?growthPercentage >= 1)
}
